---
title: Korean-Style Fish & Garlic Rice with Sesame Veggies & Plant-Based Mayo
description: If you're familiar with bibimbap, the Korean “mixed rice” dish, then you'll love this HelloFresh plant-based version. So, divvy up the fragrant rice, pile on the fish and toppings, then mix it all together for a glorious fusion of flavours and textures.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67ca5321c2f2c4b379aae6bd-9e677995.jpeg
